4.

00:01:25.680 --> 00:01:26.680
They're Not a 24-7 Job

00:01:26.680 --> 00:01:27.680
Grownup dogs don't require the constant monitoring
puppies do, leaving you with more freedom

00:01:27.680 --> 00:01:28.680
to do your own thing.

00:01:28.680 --> 00:01:29.680
If you have young children, or just value
your "me time," this is definitely a bonus.

00:01:29.680 --> 00:01:30.680
5.

00:01:30.680 --> 00:01:31.680
They Settle in Quickly

00:01:31.680 --> 00:01:32.680
Older dogs have been around the block and
already learned what it takes to get along

00:01:32.680 --> 00:01:34.569
with others and become part of a pack.

00:01:34.569 --> 00:01:36.619
They'll be part of the family in no time!

