00:01:40.040 --> 00:01:41.040
6.

00:01:41.040 --> 00:01:42.040
Fewer Messes

00:01:42.040 --> 00:01:43.040
Your floors, shoes and furniture will thank
you for adopting a senior pooch!

00:01:43.040 --> 00:01:44.040
Older dogs are likely to already be housetrained
- and even if they're not, they have the physical

00:01:44.040 --> 00:01:45.040
and mental abilities to pick it up really
fast (unlike puppies).

00:01:45.040 --> 00:01:46.040
With their teething years far behind them,
seniors also are much less likely to be destructive

00:01:46.040 --> 00:01:47.040
chewers.

00:01:47.040 --> 00:01:48.040
7.

00:01:48.040 --> 00:01:49.040
You Won't Bite Off More Than You Can Chew

00:01:49.040 --> 00:01:50.420
There are those who yearn for a doggie friend
of their own, but hold back because they worry

00:01:50.420 --> 00:01:51.970
what might happen in their lives in the years
to come.

00:01:51.970 --> 00:01:57.770
And they are wise to do so - a puppy or young
dog can be anywhere from an 8- to 20-year

00:01:57.770 --> 00:02:06.590
responsibility, which is not appropriate for
the very elderly or those with certain long-term

00:02:06.590 --> 00:02:07.850
future plans.

00:02:07.850 --> 00:02:09.000
Providing a loving home for a dog in her golden
years is not a less serious commitment, but

00:02:09.000 --> 00:02:10.000
it can be a shorter one.

00:02:10.000 --> 00:02:11.000
8.

00:02:11.000 --> 00:02:12.000
They Enjoy Easy Livin'

00:02:12.000 --> 00:02:13.000
Couch potato, know thyself!

00:02:13.000 --> 00:02:14.000
Please consider a canine retiree rather than
a high-energy young dog who will run you ragged.

00:02:14.000 --> 00:02:15.000
Not that older dogs don't require any exercise
- they do - but they're not going to need,

00:02:15.000 --> 00:02:20.459
or want, to run a marathon every day.

00:02:20.459 --> 00:02:22.709
9.

00:02:22.709 --> 00:02:40.040
Save a Life, Be a Hero

00:02:40.040 --> 00:03:29.269
At shelters, older dogs are often the last
to be adopted and the first to be euthanized.

00:03:29.269 --> 00:03:30.269
Saving an animal's life offers an unparalleled
emotional return on your investment, and you'll

00:03:30.269 --> 00:03:31.269
feel the rewards every day you spend together.

